      "summary": "Anthropic LLM Provider 类。构造函数创建 RouteClient（默认 baseUrl: api.anthropic.com，自动附加 x-api-key 和 anthropic-version 头）。stream 方法构建包含 system 字段的请求体，通过 RouteClient.postStream 发送到 /v1/messages 端点，反序列化 Anthropic SSE 事件。错误处理区分超时、认证、限流和通用错误。",
      "tags": [
        "provider",
        "anthropic",
        "claude",
        "streaming",
        "exported"
      ],
      "complexity": "medium"
    },
    {
      "id": "b8:file:provider-openai-compatible",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "providers/openai-compatible.ts",
      "filePath": "packages/core/src/llm/providers/openai-compatible.ts",
      "summary": "通用 OpenAI 兼容 Provider 适配器，提供 OpenAICompatibleProvider 类。支持 DeepSeek、Ollama、Groq、Fireworks、Together AI、Cerebras、xAI、Perplexity 等第三方 Provider。复用 openai-compatible-chat 协议的序列化/反序列化函数。添加新 Provider 只需在 providers/index.ts 中新增配置即可，无需编写代码。",
      "tags": [
        "llm",
        "provider",
        "openai-compatible",
        "deepseek",
        "ollama",
        "generic"
      ],
      "complexity": "medium"
    },
    {
      "id": "b8:class:OpenAICompatibleProvider",
      "type": "class",
      "name": "OpenAICompatibleProvider",
      "filePath": "packages/core/src/llm/providers/openai-compatible.ts",
      "summary": "通用 OpenAI 兼容 Provider 类。构造函数接收 CompatibleProviderConfig（扩展 RouteConfig，增加 name 属性）。stream 方法与 OpenAIProvider 类似，构建请求体->通过 RouteClient.postStream 发送到 /chat/completions->反序列化为 LLMEvent。错误处理较简单（仅区分超时和通用错误）。",
      "tags": [
        "provider",
        "openai-compatible",
        "streaming",
        "exported"
      ],
      "complexity": "medium"
    },
